    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014it\u2019s in absolutely gorgeous, pristine condition. You\u2019ll be hard-pressed to find a single blemish; she shines just like the day she rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling without the dealership headache, this is the one. Come by, have a coffee, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your next favorite memory!",
